data.description: Calling All BUYERS... Preferably Cash buyers that can seize this AMAZING /great opportunity fast! Sellers are under contract on a new build and must meet their closing deadline of 3/11/2024. Price dropped to reflect their motivation to sell now! RVM is 388K. You buy and keep the equity! Call us and submit your offer now. Amazing home in Silver Creek Hills SD!!! Can you believe this great opportunity? That's right!  Only minutes from the highway, this great home is an awesome location from the city and more! Gracing the market is this awesome 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath, split-bedroom floor plan, boasting high ceilings, an eat-in kitchen & a separate dining room, family room with a gas starter fireplace, perfect for these chilly Georgia days/evenings, upper-level laundry room for your convenience, double vanity/soaking tub, separate shower and more. A 2-car garage & a back patio area, enter from your garage into an open foyer, spacious rooms throughout and more. Walk in and fall in love with how you can make a few minor upgrades and make this home practically new. The sellers' have already completed the work of a new roof (less than 1 year ago) a new gas water heater (less than 1 year ago), freshly painted lower level, freshly shampooed carpet and more, this gem is move-in ready. Let Cupid have his way and schedule your touring experience today! Showings by appointment only. Special hours noted in the private remarks. Owner occupied and owners have a new baby, so ssshhh... tip toe in and make your best offer but hurry this one won't last long!!
